<title>USA: AMEX closing averages.</title>
<headline>AMEX closing averages.</headline>
<dateline>NEW YORK 1997-05-02</dateline>
<text>
<p>Prices on the American Stock Exchange closed higher in moderate trading.</p>
<p>The Amex Composite index closed at 568.50, up 10.00.</p>
<p>Winners beat losers 397 to 159.</p>
<p>The average price per share was up $0.23.</p>
<p>Preliminary volume was 18,786,100 compared with 20,427,090 on Thursday.</p>
<p>(Prices official as of 1630 EST/2130 GMT)</p>
<p>((-- Wall Street desk, 212-859-1730))</p>
